N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 211.16 - People in boxer's corner

State Regulations

Each boxer shall submit to the Commission for approval the
name of his or her chief second and assistant seconds and no one other than
approved seconds shall be permitted in the corner of the
boxer. Notes
